  english: Summons sharp bamboo spikes from the ground. Deals massive AoE damage
    and knocks up enemies. Has a long cooldown.
  vietnamese: "G\u1ECDi ch\xF4ng tre m\u1ECDc b\xF9ng l\xEAn t\u1EEB l\xF2ng \u0111\u1EA5t
    trong m\u1ED9t khu v\u1EF1c. G\xE2y s\xE1t th\u01B0\u01A1ng di\u1EC7n r\u1ED9ng
    v\xE0 h\u1EA5t tung qu\xE1i v\u1EADt. Th\u1EDDi gian h\u1ED3i chi\xEAu l\xE2u."
